<title>LogicGrid 11.0.3</title>
<sparkle:version>11003</sparkle:version>
<sparkle:shortVersionString>11.0.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
<sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
<description><![CDATA[<h3>Bug Fix</h3>
<p>Fixed a sneaky yet annoying bug that sometimes caused the grid to disappear when a plugin window or Logic menu window was open for more than 20 seconds.</p>
<h3>Other Improvements</h3>
<p>The Keyboard Shortcuts menu items are now clickable. Clicking does the same thing as the keyboard shortcut.</p>]]></description>
